"""
CallCare — STRICT Evidence via OpenAI web_search (Python 3.9 safe)

CRITICAL POLICY:
- Only accept authoritative guideline/public health sources OR peer-reviewed repositories.
- No consumer/blog/AI content farms.

EvidenceRef schema in this codebase is ONLY:
  - title
  - source
  - snippet
So we store "URL | Accessed YYYY-MM-DD" in snippet.
"""

